Horizontal vs Vertical Scaling
Ways to improve performance of an application - 
  - Tune the application and improve design.
  - Vertical scaling. Adding resources to the server.
  - Adding servers to support the existing database.

Partitioning data in a SQL database is very hard.

This video gives a good run down of the trade offs involved in scaling databases.

https://www.infoq.com/presentations/database-scalability-techniques/

